reated":1546601570,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a0b38f435e557e3b43687517e25b59de?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a0b38f435e557e3b43687517e25b59de?s=24&d=retro","location":"","btc":"","id":375269},"last_reply_by":"DylanZ","last_touched":1629081833,"title":"部分 App“屏蔽”了 iOS 的大致位置功能","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/795970","created":1629074481,"content":"发现一些 App 请求权限的时候，如果用户不授权允许精确位置而只授权大致位置，那么它们就会像完全没有授予位置权限那样请求用户开启权限，而不会去使用 iOS 给出的大致位置。\r\n\r\n目前遇到的有：Lyft, Starbucks\r\n\r\n不过有些 App 则反之，只申请大致位置，比如哔哩哔哩会员购界面","content_rendered":"<p>发现一些 App 请求权限的时候，如果用户不授权允许精确位置而只授权大致位置，那么它们就会像完全没有授予位置权限那样请求用户开启权限，而不会去使用 iOS 给出的大致位置。</p>\n<p>目前遇到的有：Lyft, Starbucks</p>\n<p>不过有些 App 则反之，只申请大致位置，比如哔哩哔哩会员购界面</p>\n","last_modified":1629074481,"replies":18,"id":795970},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_large.png?m=1588961795","name":"router","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_normal.png?m=1588961795","title":"路由器","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/router","topics":1113,"footer":"","header":"数据包流动的乐趣","title_alternative":"Router","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_mini.png?m=1588961795","stars":1374,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":824,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"ztxgeol","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e6d3/2d8f/120249_mini.png?m=1501556336","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ztxgeol","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1433258336,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e6d3/2d8f/120249_mini.png?m=1501556336","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e6d3/2d8f/120249_mini.png?m=1501556336","location":"","btc":"","id":120249},"last_reply_by":"lsylsy2","last_touched":1629082073,"title":"x86 路由器推荐","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/795969","created":1629073094,"content":"ISP: 950/500\r\n\r\n求推荐一款 x86 router，在墙外没有 fq 需求，就想 local DNS server like AdGuardHome，可以去广告.\r\n\r\nCurrently running a rb750Gr3 with openwrt+simple-adblock.\r\n\r\n但是 openwrt 很 buggy，hwnat 会经常 kernel panic，network 也是.\r\n\r\n所以现在只想要 x86platform 装 lunix，也不太想要 arm:(","content_rendered":"<p>ISP: 950/500</p>\n<p>求推荐一款 x86 router，在墙外没有 fq 需求，就想 local DNS server like AdGuardHome，可以去广告.</p>\n<p>Currently running a rb750Gr3 with openwrt+simple-adblock.</p>\n<p>但是 openwrt 很 buggy，hwnat 会经常 kernel panic，network 也是.</p>\n<p>所以现在只想要 x86platform 装 lunix，也不太想要 arm:(</p>\n","last_modified":1629073094,"replies":18,"id":795969},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1628872948","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1628872948","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":45377,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1628872948","stars":7477,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"username":"shijingshijing","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d9cb/7b26/149367_mini.png?m=1474282431","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shijingshijing","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1448898993,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d9cb/7b26/149367_mini.png?m=1474282431","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d9cb/7b26/149367_mini.png?m=1474282431","location":"","btc":"","id":149367},"last_reply_by":"dfkjgklfdjg","last_touched":1629084892,"title":"千万不要手贱升级 Firefox 91 版， Proton 禁用也无法换回原来的 Tab 栏了。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/795994","created":1629079397,"content":"Proton 目前个人感觉很耗资源，禁用后速度有明显提升，而且 Proton 的 Tab 占据太多空间，以前很多基于 Firefox 的 UI 测试直接无法运行。\r\n\r\nFirefox 91 之前的版本，包括默认启用 Proton 的 Firefox 90 版本，都可以在 about:config 里面 disable 掉 Proton，从而恢复成原来紧凑的模式，如下图所示：\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xOGs3LF.png\" />\r\n\r\n更新到 91 版之后，即使是 disable 掉了 Proton，紧凑的 Tab 栏也回不去了，如下图所示：\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3U6qS7W.png\" />\r\n\r\n目前在网上找了一圈，github 上有个 Firefox UI 用自定义的方式实现了类似的风格，但是是在启用 Proton 的条件下（原文没仔细看，好象是利用 Proton 能自定义界面的特性实现的），跟以前紧凑的风格明显不一样，而且能感觉明显卡顿。网址： https://github.com/black7375/Firefox-UI-Fix 显示风格如下：\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S3pgIL4.png\" />","content_rendered":"<p>Proton 目前个人感觉很耗资源，禁用后速度有明显提升，而且 Proton 的 Tab 占据太多空间，以前很多基于 Firefox 的 UI 测试直接无法运行。</p>\n<p>Firefox 91 之前的版本，包括默认启用 Proton 的 Firefox 90 版本，都可以在 about:config 里面 disable 掉 Proton，从而恢复成原来紧凑的模式，如下图所示：\n<img class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xOGs3LF.png\"/></p>\n<p>更新到 91 版之后，即使是 disable 掉了 Proton，紧凑的 Tab 栏也回不去了，如下图所示：\n<img class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3U6qS7W.png\"/></p>\n<p>目前在网上找了一圈，github 上有个 Firefox UI 用自定义的方式实现了类似的风格，但是是在启用 Proton 的条件下（原文没仔细看，好象是利用 Proton 能自定义界面的特性实现的），跟以前紧凑的风格明显不一样，而且能感觉明显卡顿。网址： <a href=\"https://github.com/black7375/Firefox-UI-Fix\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/black7375/Firefox-UI-Fix</a> 显示风格如下：</p>\n<img class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S3pgIL4.png\"/>","last_modified":1629079397,"replies":10,"id":795994},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_large.png?m=1624089774","name":"security","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_normal.png?m=1624089774","title":"信息安全","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/security","topics":1211,"footer":"","header":"我们都希望自己管理的计算机系统在运转过程中不要遇到任何安全事件。只是，这个不完美的世界的现实告诉我们：学无止境。","title_alternative":"Security","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1624089774","stars":1341,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":260,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"1sm23","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f4b2c664d46b2f68c3d4848c4c73f72d?s=24&d=retro","bio"